body:
Added a function that can automatically generate TypeScript type by loading JSON data.

It is generated by entering JSON in the form below.

List type, JSON key escape is an issue, but I think it is easy to use when you want to generate a type easily.

[URL] (https://portal.kemu.site/tools/jsonTyper)

---

